message.body: Those jerks didn't even tell me they posted this! Have an interview at Rowan next week what should I do for my production presentation for 45 minutes?

They are weird like that! I wonder if they already have someone. You should build stairs from grip materials! I stressed like hell over my presentation lastbyear and am game to talk through if you want! Is it to be in your own work?
They are being super quiet about it. I'm ready to leave soon I think. Yeah maybe I can show them how to use a yoga mat as a dolly. I have THREE presentations. What the duck
Are you around today? Might give you a call and see what you did for your interview.
Yep, i am! I'll be off the train in 5 minutes, then around all day. Production is tough.
Cool. I have to call Rowan at 10 to get some details I'll call you after!
